#

Pan-Seared New York Steak with Red Wine Reduction and Truffle Mashed Potatoes

$35
850 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

GourmetSteakComfort Food

Description

Indulge in a succulent New York steak, perfectly seared and paired with a rich red wine reduction, complemented by creamy truffle-infused mashed potatoes.

Ingredients

  • New York Strip Steak: 2 (8 oz each)
  • Red Wine: 1 cup
  • Beef Broth: 1/2 cup
  • Shallots: 2, finely chopped
  • Fresh Thyme: 1 sprig
  • Butter: 2 tbsp
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Potatoes: 2 lbs, peeled and cubed
  • Heavy Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Truffle Oil: 1 tbsp
  • Parmesan Cheese: 1/4 cup, grated
